  <sect3>
    <title>Overview</title>
    <para>
      The <ulink url="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/JPEG_2000">JPEG 2000</ulink>
      format was developed to succeed JPEG. It supports both lossy and
      lossless compression, and high dynamic range images.
      <acronym>GIMP</acronym> also has an
      <link linkend="file-heif-hej2-export">exporter</link> for storing a JPEG 2000
      image inside a HEIF container.
    </para>
